VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT \brand::random\s*\(\)|\bthread_rng\s*\(\)
WHEN EXPR MISSING:OsRng|rand_core::OsRng|getrandom|os_rng && MISSING:simulation|game|test|example
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects generic randomness usage that may be misused in security-sensitive flows.
TRACE Externalized rule logic for Weak Randomness Source.
